[30;1m138 | [0m[35m<p>Because you usually have a large number of duplicated IP addresses that you[0m
[30;1m139 | [0m[35mwant to check, this function makes the process practical and efficient, in[0m
[30;1m140 | [0m[35mcomparison to running the command thousands of times from the comand line.</p>[0m
